  ues_usage_setting, int, "标识REGISTRATION REQUEST消息中“UE's usage setting”IE中“UE's usage setting”信息，取值：\n0：voice centric\n1：data centric\n取值参见3GPP 24.501 第9.11.3.55节", null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null
